t activity, upstream trace errors, and response metric anomalies), determined cause is [adservice-getRandomAds-latency & rrt & rrt_max] (From Ground Truth).\nActionable Checks:\nCheck Log: Search for keyword \'AdService-getRandomAds-latency\' in logs from pod \'adservice-0\'.\nCheck Log: Search for keyword \'DeadlineExceeded\' in logs, particularly from frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2).\nCheck Log: Search for keyword \'InvocationTargetException\' in logs from pod \'adservice-0\'.\nCheck Log: Search for keyword \'transform\' in logs from pod \'adservice-0\'.\nCheck Trace: Check trace data for operations \'hipstershop.AdService/GetAds\' with parent_pod being frontend instances (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) and status \'context deadline exceeded\'.\nCheck Metric: Query metrics \'rrt\' and \'rrt_max\' for service_name=\'adservice\' and pod_name=\'adservice-0\' during the fault time range.', 'metadata': {'num_checks': 6, 'fault_type': 'adservice-getRandomAds-latency & rrt & rrt_max', 'num_reasoning_steps': 8, 'symptom_vector': 'High JVM latency causing response delays and elevated request latency.', 'uuid': '74bd0298-209', 'root_cause_desc': 'Component [adservice-0] experienced [adservice-getRandomAds-latency & rrt & rrt_max] fault.', 'modalities': 'Trace,Log,Metric'}, 'distance': 0.857574462890625}, {'uuid': '9a257bd5-150', 'document': 'Fault Type: adservice-getRandomAds-latency, rrt, rrt_max\nSymptom: High JVM latency, JVM response delay, elevated request latency, and JVM slow response.\nRoot Cause: Component [adservice] experienced [adservice-getRandomAds-latency, rrt, rrt_max] fault.\nReasoning: Step 1: Check Metadata - Confirm faulty component is [adservice] (From Ground Truth). Step 2: Check Observation - Found keyword [adservice-getRandomAds-latency] in Log (From GT key_observations), as seen in log entries like \'AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749399002 execute()\'. Step 3: Check Observation - Found keyword [deadlineexceeded] in Log (Fro